that should not have been forgotten...

58
00:05:33,390 --> 00:05:36,489
...were lost.

59
00:05:36,490 --> 00:05:38,989
History became legend...

60
00:05:38,990 --> 00:05:41,189
...legend became myth.

61
00:05:41,190 --> 00:05:44,289
And for two and a half thousand years...

62
00:05:44,290 --> 00:05:48,589
... the ring passed out of all knowledge.

63
00:05:48,590 --> 00:05:52,089
Until, when chance came...

64
00:05:52,090 --> 00:05:56,590
