of the Misty Mountains.

69
00:06:08,590 --> 00:06:11,689
And there it consumed him.

70
00:06:11,690 --> 00:06:13,889
It came to me.

71
00:06:13,890 --> 00:06:18,589
My own. My love. My own.

72
00:06:18,590 --> 00:06:24,590
My precious.

73
00:06:26,890 --> 00:06:30,599
The ring brought to Gollum unnatural long life.

74
00:06:30,600 --> 00:06:34,489
For 500 years it poisoned his mind.

75
00:06:34,490 --> 00:06:39,299
And in the gloom of Gollum's cave, it waited.

76
00:06:39,300 --> 00:06:42,899
Darkness crept back into the forests of the world.

77
00:06:42,900 --> 00:06:45,899
Rumor grew of a shadow in the East...

78
00:06:45,900 --> 00:06:48,899
... whispers of a nameless fear.

79
00:06:48,900 --> 00:06:52,499
And the ring of power perceived...

80
00:06:52,500 --> 00:06:56,600
...its time had now come.

81
00:06:57,700 --> 00:07:00,999
It abandoned Gollum.

82
00:07:01,000 --> 00:07:06,299
But something happened then
the ring did not intend.

83
00:07:06,300 --> 00:07:11,099
It was picked up by the most
unlikely creature imaginable.

84
00:07:11,100 --> 00:07:12,399
What's this?

85
00:07:12,400 --> 00:07:13,899
A hobbit.

86
00:07:13,900 --> 00:07:16,999
Bilbo Baggins of the Shire.

87
00:07:17,000 --> 00:07:18,899
A ring.

88
00:07:18,900 --> 00:07:22,200
Lost!

89
00:07:23,500 --> 00:07:27,199
My precious is lost!

90
00:07:27,200 --> 00:07:29,799
